text: Rahul V Raj (born May 26,1992 in Thrithallur, Thrissur) is an Indian footballer who plays as a defender for Kerala football team in 2018. He was the Captain, who led the team Kerala to win against West Bengal by scoring penalty point in 2018 Santosh Trophy Final. == References == == Other websites == *Rahul V Raj at Multisports Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Indian footballers Category:Association football defenders
